        <abstract>
            <p>At Wallace’s suggestion he offers CD his observations on the seed-gathering habits of ants. Suggests their role in seed dispersal.</p> 
<p>At work on the last part of his book [<hi rend="italic">Contributions to the flora of Mentone</hi> (1867–71)].</p>  
<p>Has found that <hi rend="italic">Ophrys insectifera</hi> can reproduce asexually.</p> 
        </abstract>
